{"tid":2441263,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"海外港人成立廣東話社企平台「DNLM」 提供移民生活資訊 幫助同路人適應海外生活","createTime":"2021-03-10T14:14:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T20:27:51.000Z","uid":63183,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d18e9bcf12b7c48ec0de02dc743ad80fd802743e","tid":2441263,"uid":63183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T14:14:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cpwZWNA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcpwZWNA.png&h=000700bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nsource:<a href=\"https://gongjyuhok.hk/articles/5813\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgongjyuhok.hk%2Farticles%2F5813&d=86rwbh%2BN0C2BU4li7ttIPi%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=52a71a0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://gongjyuhok.hk/articles/5813</a><br />\n<br />\n最近有海外港人成立生活指南網站，為有意移民嘅港人提供生活資訊，希望凝聚香港人力量，秉承助人自助精神。呢個平台就係完全用廣東話書寫、以社企形式運作嘅DNLM Directory (Delay No-more Listing Master) 。<br />\n<br />\n平台由十幾歲移民美國嘅「十三妹」同「毒南」創立。佢哋話用DNLM呢個名除咗要表達「對社會嘅憤怒」，都希望加入香港本土元素：「我哋想喺個名唔提香港，但可以俾人一眼便睇出（個網）同香港有關。」<br />\n<br />\n佢哋話希望提供香港人免費買賣個人以至商業產品嘅平台，拓展海外香港人市場；而且希望打破香港人之間嘅同溫層，鼓勵香港人探索新嘢。<br />\n<br />\n佢哋又話，會將收入扣除必要開支用作幫助同路人適應海外生活，同埋聘請同路人。佢哋暫時服務地區包括美國、英國、加拿大、台灣、德國同澳洲。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rNs23xYt4aM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrNs23xYt4aM&d=86rwbh%2BN0C2BU4li7ttIPi%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=6389c922\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rNs23xYt4aM</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://dnlmdirectory.com/HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdnlmdirectory.com%2FHK&d=86rwbh%2BN0C2BU4li7ttIPi%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=e2e34067\" target=\"_blank\">https://dnlmdirectory.com/HK</a>"},{"pid":"d9c1ebdaaf0868de6dfd41c94c2b5fadd61d008e","tid":2441263,"uid":40369,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T14:17:42.000Z","msg":"用依d 名第一個感覺似班nmslese"},{"pi